featured_reviews.review_id:
Masjid e Gareeb Nawaz is a purely Sunni Masjid, which is run by Dawat-e-Islami in a very successful manner.
It is situated at "Gali no.11, Export Market", i recommend you to kindly visit this mosque because the professionals here are higly skilled and smart, who convey their message in a peaceful manner.
On Jummeraat after Isha Salah, there is an Ijtema_paak, which is programmed regularly where Naat Shareef are being recited, a highly qualified personals are invited to speak and share the sunnah of Islam, followed by bayan and Duas.
This mosque is really very awesome you must visit.
The timing for Jumma is at 1:30, but to avail the seat in the first floor and gain more sawaab you must reach as early as possible.

Regards: Imran (Student_DU)
